
This directory contains specific data collection programs and a directory
(senders) that contains code for the remote devices that feed these
programs.

Sub-directories:

  get_resp - basic logging program.  Parks itself on a serial port listening
    for data then logs it appropiately.

  cmd_resp - basic logging program with the ability to send simple commands
    back to the remote device.

  axon - provides an interactive connection to a remote node via the serial
    port.

  senders - a directory containing various codes for making the appropiate
    remote data collection and sending nodes.
